::Killfest::

Killfest watches Speedbreaker hit the ground. His jetpack sputters 
and gives out, sending him flying down. He hits the ground at an 
angle, rolling before jumping to his feet and looking around for 
Speedbreaker.



--- In nbwrpg@y..., Jeremiah <rdahl@s...> wrote:
> "Uh, yeah," he says between puff, trying to put out the flames. He 
lets go
> of Killfest, and transforms back to car mode. Still on fire, he 
races to
> the ground, Gravity pulling him hard. He hits the ground hard, but 
the
> speed of his decent puts out the fire. He drives forward, following
> Killfest from below.
